t: "They say ňĻto the Prophetňļ, ‚ÄúIf we were to follow ňĻtrueňļ guidance with you, we would certainly be snatched away from our land.‚ÄĚ Have We not established for them a safe haven ňĻin Meccaňļ to which fruits of all kinds are brought as a provision from Us? But most of them do not know ňĻthis favourňļ"